high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove top, facing the toaster.
Pick up the knife that is to the right of the toaster.
Turn left, walking past the stove top towards the fridge.  Then turn right around the edge of the counter towards the door.  Turn to face the short edge of the counter.
Slice half of the loaf of bread that is on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.  Face the fridge.
Open the fridge (bottom door), slice half of the loaf of bread that is sitting on the top shelf, then close the fridge door.
Still holding the knife, turn left and walk to the wall, then turn left again and walk to the trash can that sits in the corner.
Put the knife into the trash can to the right of the green apple.
Turn around and walk past the fridge towards the door, stopping to face the short edge of the counter that is to the right of the door.
Pick up one slice of bread from off of the counter.
Turn right and walk to the trash can (walk past the fridge to the wall, then turn left to go to the trash can in the corner).
Put the slice of bread into the trash can in front of the bottle.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge (bottom) door, take out one slice of bread from the top shelf, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk back to the trash can that is in the corner along the wall.
Put the slice of bread into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and two slices of bread into a trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and walk past the counter and then turn around to the right to face the end of the counter.
Cut the bread on the end of the counter into slices.
Turn to the right and walk forward and turn right to face the fridge.
Cut the loaf of bread in the fridge into slices.
Turn right and walk to the wall, then turn left and walk forward to face the trash can on the floor.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room to the end of the counter and turn right to face then end of the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the wall, then turn left and walk forward to face the trash can on the floor.
Place the slice of bread in the trash can.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room to the fridge and then turn left to face the fridge.
Pick up a slice of bread from inside the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the wall, then turn left and walk forward to face the trash can on the floor.
Place the slice of bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To put two slices of bread from two different loaves into the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the toaster.
Pick up the knife from the counter next to the toaster.
Turn left and walk to the loaf of bread.
Slice the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open and look in the refrigerator and close it again.
Walk to the wall, then turn left to go to the trash can.
Put the knife in the trash can.
Turn around and walk across the room to the sliced loaf of bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the loaf on the counter.
Walk across the room to the trash can.
Put the slice of bread in the trash can.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Take a slice of bread out of the refrigerator.
Turn around and walk back to the trash can.
Put the slice of bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put several items in the trash can.
